## Short Description for GitHub / YouTube Draft

Episode 1 introduces the central puzzle of the series: how civilization continues despite the uncertainty of human behaviour. By comparing biological, physical, and social systems, the episode shows that human societies depend on ongoing participation rather than embedded structure alone. This leads to the key insight that people must form expectations under uncertainty by relying on traces of past behaviour. The episode ends by setting up the next chapter: the trust signal.
